  physical_appearance: This is an orange cheongsam and it is sleeveless. There is a collar present as well. There are no visible tears on the exterior of the cheongsam. There are red
 light oranger
 and purple coloured floral motifs appearing all over the cheongsam. They come in different shapes and sizes. The piping of the cheongsam runs from the collar to its left side
 just below its left arm hole.
